{"type":"message","id":"0b7a881e","parentId":"9aa0f431","timestamp":"2026-03-09T21:10:42.985Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here are the top 10 highest-signal job roles available tonight from your local data, with company, title, brief why-fit, and urgency score (1-5):\n\n1. Company: Welo Data  \n   Title: AI Internet Rater  \n   Why-fit: Relevant for AI/machine learning interest; score 2 indicates moderate priority  \n   Urgency: 2\n\n2. Company: ELEMENTAL TERRA CAPITAL LTD  \n   Title: Entry-Level Crypto Market Specialist  \n   Why-fit: Good entry-level role in crypto market with global reach  \n   Urgency: 1\n\n3. Company: XXIX  \n   Title: Senior Product Designer  \n   Why-fit: Fits design seniority with worldwide remote availability  \n   Urgency: 1\n\n4. Company: Lemon.io  \n   Title: Senior Full-stack React Developer  \n   Why-fit: Senior React dev position, broad geographic hiring (Americas, Europe, Asia, Oceania)  \n   Urgency: 1\n\n5. Company: Nebulab  \n   Title: Shopify Engineer  \n   Why-fit: Software role focused on Shopify platform, worldwide open  \n   Urgency: 1\n\n6. Company: GNO Partners  \n   Title: Senior Amazon Brand Manager  \n   Why-fit: Marketing role with Amazon brand focus, good seniority  \n   Urgency: 1\n\n7. Company: Lumitekno Kreasi Global  \n   Title: Red Team Specialist (Offensive Security)  \n   Why-fit: Cybersecurity offense role, worldwide remote  \n   Urgency: 1\n\n8. Company: shopware AG  \n   Title: AI-Native Cloud Infrastructure Generalist (m/f/d)  \n   Why-fit: AI cloud generalist role in Europe/Germany, good fit for AI/cloud experience  \n   Urgency: 1\n\n9. Company: Clipboard Health  \n   Title: Client Support Specialist  \n   Why-fit: Client support role across diverse regions, good for customer service skills  \n   Urgency: 1\n\n10. Company: Mitre Media  \n    Title: Tech Lead Full-Stack Rails Engineer  \n    Why-fit: Leadership role in full-stack Rails dev for USA/Canada, good seniority and tech stack  \n    Urgency: 1\n\nMost roles have urgency score 1 except the AI Internet Rater role which is slightly higher at 2. These are actionable leads to pursue now for immediate job momentum. Let me know if you want help with specific applications or other details.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0b9a1a829e838ec60069af3742492881928346d1e3421d9a2f\"}"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openai","model":"gpt-4.1-mini","usage":{"input":1962,"output":504,"cacheRead":11136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13602,"cost":{"input":0.0007848000000000001,"output":0.0008064000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0011136000000000002,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0027048000000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773090624740}}
